About 
Ben Dinnery is football’s leading injury specialist. The ‘go-to’ guru for big hitters like Sky Sports, ESPN and NBC Sports when they need data. Or the BBC, talkSPORT and the broadsheets when a quote is required. His unique insight has helped provide a better understanding of what is really happening in the treatment rooms.

Jason McKenna has a focus on tactics and data to contextualise injury news. He is a 2 time award winning Radio Presenter and has a history of studying football.  He is also currently researching a PhD showing his dedication to high quality analysis.

Premier Injuries is the go to resource for injury related data pertaining to the English Premier League. The company’s database contains detailed analysis of every reported player injury since establishment back in 2010.
